3e67746d3c9c9e5823","tid":1765464,"uid":21873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T01:36:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f56390171e0c4411b4ac59e788968ef0c4f25cc","tid":1765464,"uid":21873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T01:42:19.000Z","msg":"求幫推,解答我疑惑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c589226316f30a4787e834c8efe142b3aaa932c5","tid":1765464,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T01:47:52.000Z","msg":"黃絲錢真係易呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f9239ce6b9e4b90ef5404ca43d04a0eab16087","tid":1765464,"uid":69177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T01:49:03.000Z","msg":"兩個唔同團隊黎架<br />\n你第一條LINK個POST都有提催淚之城 (催淚之城=籌夠錢但唔夠人氣果個團隊)"},{"pid":"12c9370bc2ebea260a765b3011860285794d72c2","tid":1765464,"uid":69177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T01:51:37.000Z","msg":"FYI<br />\n<br />\n[要人］另一條紀錄片《2019：夏日宣言》開始眾籌！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1701487\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1701487</a>"},{"pid":"cbceb48bce0c4a0cbf97dbd7b4e8a99597067ff6","tid":1765464,"uid":276812,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T04:11:59.000Z","msg":"你文盲定係弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兩班唔同人黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下from夏日宣言團隊<br />\n<br />\n//對不起，我們眾籌失敗了！<br />\n<br />\n感謝大家連日來的支持和信任，《2019：夏日宣言》（The Edge of Liberty）製作團隊目前在眾籌平台籌得超過40萬，接近1000人成為backers，惟距離目標金額（170萬）仍有一大段差距，我們宣佈是次眾籌失敗。<br />\n<br />\n由於是次眾籌未能達標，根據Kickstarter眾籌平台的條款(達標後才會於backers戶口扣減款項)，意味本團隊於是次眾籌活動不會獲得任何款項。<br />\n<br />\n經我們團隊檢討先前的不足後， 我們會再接再厲，重整宣傳工作及籌備重新眾籌，希望完成紀錄片製作，將香港反送中抗爭呈現國際。<br />\n<br />\n至本團隊眾籌開始，很榮幸地得到不少媒體業界及志同道合者的支持，主動為我們提供器材及人力支援，減省部分製作成本。因此，第二輪眾籌將會降低目標金額，務求可以盡快達標並開始後期工作。<br />\n<br />\n另外，為了解答大家的疑問/對於部分支持者的疑問，我們必須重申/澄清以下幾點：<br />\n<br />\n1）根據Kickstarter眾籌平台，一切款項只會在眾籌數目達標後，才會於backers戶口扣減款項。換言之，所有已認投的backers不會被扣除任何款項，而本團隊亦不會從中獲得任何款項。<br />\n<br />\n2）由於預期是次眾籌於到期日不會達標，本團隊亦會停止Kickstarter眾籌之宣傳活動 。 <br />\n<br />\n3）新一輪的眾籌活動將於半個月內開展，並於Kickstarter或其他眾籌平台舉行，視乎眾籌平台審批結果而定。如想了解最新情況，請留意以下平台：<br />\n<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/theedgeofliberty/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftheedgeofliberty%2F&d=uyenQRwN%2F2p2tRNf%2Bb8L0QX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=12d4671f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/theedgeofliberty/</a><br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://www.twitter.com/edgeoflibertyhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitter.com%2Fedgeoflibertyhk&d=uyenQRwN%2F2p2tRNf%2Bb8L0QX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=20361960\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitter.com/edgeoflibertyhk</a><br />\nTelegram: <a href=\"https://t.me/theedgeofliberty\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftheedgeofliberty&d=uyenQRwN%2F2p2tRNf%2Bb8L0QX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=75944996\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/theedgeofliberty</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/teol_hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fteol_hk%2F&d=uyenQRwN%2F2p2tRNf%2Bb8L0QX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=c978ec12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/teol_hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n最後，本團隊再次感謝一眾支持者，我們將再度歸來，希望大家日後能繼續支持我們。如有造成任何不便，希望各位能夠諒解。<br />\n<br />\n#光復香港時代革命<br />\n#香港人加油<br />\n//"},{"pid":"69387f68477e9cdf195a26a42f629bab385fb956","tid":1765464,"uid":276812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T04:16:40.000Z","msg":"Kickstarter 係籌唔達標 就一蚊都拎唔到"},{"pid":"2beb1dab16c425a28c3d2705c1f26983c59fdb75","tid":1765464,"uid":276812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T04:21:53.000Z","msg":"//因為我有份捐錢所以都幾記得好快就夠左錢仲突左勁多<br />\n之後仲話唔缺錢想捐小小10蚊咁整大個人數//<br />\n<br />\n你講緊嗰個催淚之城"}]}